Introduction

n.SSign (Net of Star Sign) is a nine-member boy group under n.CH Entertainment. They made their debut on August 9, 2023, with the mini album Birth Of Cosmo.

n.SSign was formed through the survival show "Stars Awakening". They began as a temporary group of seven but later became a permanent group by adding three new members.

The group name "n.SSign" is a combination of the words "new" and "star sign", which means "constellation". Each member of the group will represent an individual characteristic, forming a constellation that connects with other members and their fans (COSMO). This demonstrates their strength when they unite.

On August 5, it was announced that Member Hyun had left the group and would resign with n.CH Entertainment as an actor, and that n.SSign will continue with 9 members.

On December 9, nCH Entertainment announced that Junhyeok and Eddie, who were both on hiatus due to health concerns, would be leaving n.SSign permanently and terminating their contracts with the agency.
